OL,3,CHow people with learning disabilities
OL,4,Care being helped to cast their vote
OL,6,F"That's something that a lot of people
OL,7,Fdon't always know. The common
OL,8,Fmisconception is that people with a
OL,9,Flearning disability aren't able to
OL,10,Fvote, and that's not true."
